Class Facility

java.lang.Object
Classes.Facility
public class Facility extends Object
Facility Facility class locally stores information relevant to specific facilities data:
  • name
  • location
  • description
  • local instance of facility photo
  • list of event ids
methods include:
  • constructors
  • getters
